# Step 1: Ignore EVERYTHING by default
/*
/**

# Step 2: Allow root meta-files
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!README.md

# Step 3: Allow knowledge base zones (and all their contents)
!100-foundations/
!100-foundations/**
!200-platforms/
!200-platforms/**
!300-systems/
!300-systems/**
!400-ai-ml/
!400-ai-ml/**
!500-craft/
!500-craft/**
!800-resources/
!800-resources/**
!900-system/
!900-system/**

# Step 4: Deny dangerous patterns EVERYWHERE (even inside allowed dirs)
**/.obsidian/
**/.DS_Store
**/.claude/
**/_automation/
**/000-inbox/
**/.smart-env/
**/.trash/
**/__pycache__/
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/

# File patterns to always ignore
*.canvas
*.base
*.swp
*~
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.iml
*.pem
*.key
.env
.env.*
credentials.json
secrets.json
Thumbs.db
